#

Roasted Tomato and Feta Toast

30 min
$8.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

QuickEasyLight Meal

Description

A delightful blend of roasted tomatoes and creamy feta, served on toasted bread for a quick and satisfying bite.

Ingredients

  • cherry tomatoes: 2 cups
  • feta cheese: 1 cup, crumbled
  • sourdough bread: 4 slices
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
